# Mutually-polygamous unsatisfiable: alice is in two un-ended marriages
# (m_alice_bob, m_alice_carol) and bob is in two un-ended marriages
# (m_alice_bob, m_bob_dave). Both alice and bob are polygamy hubs;
# m_alice_bob lists alice first so bob (joining spouse) is the hub
# that should-be-host, and R14 fires on m_alice_bob alone. Swapping
# spouses there would shift the violation to alice — the configuration
# cannot be satisfied without ending one of the marriages.
person alice name:"Alice" gender:female
person bob   name:"Bob"   gender:male
person carol name:"Carol" gender:female
person dave  name:"Dave"  gender:male

marriage m_alice_bob   alice bob   start:1990-01-01
marriage m_alice_carol alice carol start:1995-03-10
marriage m_bob_dave    bob   dave  start:1997-08-22
